{"tid":2106954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係幫立場姐姐兜，但佢幾時割過本土？","createTime":"2020-07-13T14:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T14:59:34.000Z","uid":74683,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6bf350d4d61de41406291a4b0dc8de744693b9e3","tid":2106954,"uid":74683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:33:48.000Z","msg":"初選兩日佢地喺將軍澳一齊嗌咪<br />\n琴日仲出左個全投鄒家成何桂藍嘅post<br />\n<br />\n小麗老母同omdb有冇做過呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢講啲嘢係虛係無乜意思 但唔係點吸泛民黃絲票<br />\n<br />\n香港行比例代表制架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/104809544486282/posts/160507395583163/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F104809544486282%2Fposts%2F160507395583163%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=c9d8bb0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/104809544486282/posts/160507395583163/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n【新東全投抗爭派 何桂藍 鄒家成】<br />\n<br />\n立法會初選投票人數突破40萬，而家距離選舉完結仲有四個鐘，希望仍然未投票嘅市民，帶同你嘅住址證明、身分證去到新東超過50個票站投票。<br />\n<br />\n初選進入最後直路，我希望大家可以送最多抗爭派入議會。好似今日喺將軍澳嘅街站，我哋都見到年輕、抗爭派團隊的義工，好似 陳緯烈 CHAN WAI LIT 、 張偉超 、維景灣畔 葉子祈 Brandon Yip、 坑口西 余浚寧 Tsunning Yu  ， 將軍澳青年力量 TKO Pioneers 的朋友，冒住熱到中暑嘅天氣一齊嗌咪。大家不約而同咁講：今次嘅初選係一場議會路線嘅對決，究竟香港人係選擇妥協，定係選擇同共產黨正面交鋒。<br />\n<br />\n2020年香港嘅立法會，已經唔再需要立場搖擺嘅妥協派，我哋需要嘅係唔會怕踩到共產黨紅線，願意同香港人奮戰到底，以議會戰線支援街頭抗爭嘅立法會議員。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我好希望大家喺嚟緊嗰四個鐘，新東嘅朋友全投何桂藍、 鄒家成 Owen Chow 。2020年，我哋要送最多嘅抗爭派入議會，扭轉時代。"},{"pid":"ef3bfff1da22094ffed254860d0e2b89fb0f30ca","tid":2106954,"uid":74683,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:35:08.000Z","msg":"利申：投鄒家成<br />\n<br />\n但見到狙擊omdb嘅post仲立場姐姐真係笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e667827744c5fd315514883bac61d1bff08318e5","tid":2106954,"uid":74683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:35:37.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"2e027d53399c4626588e24a34c85da0aea702fe7","tid":2106954,"uid":74683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:36:24.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"a0142adfe24efd8d68a2b6a9524267e92d526cd5","tid":2106954,"uid":74683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04eb7cdc652c27a4af6e6b604917b031eeec160d","tid":2106954,"uid":69753,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:37:53.000Z","msg":"如果係立場妹妹我即投<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n立場姐姐憑麥九<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efed3ef6f0f87531800e6216ee668de6f646b058","tid":2106954,"uid":131121,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:38:22.000Z","msg":"算啦, pr當道, 連登仔普遍又缺乏批判思考<br />\n佢未當選已經假定佢一定會好似OMDB/BIG雲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但見到佢當日報道追訪, 明明見到佢果份熱情。係要老屈佢會行傳統泛民果套"},{"pid":"80277f3b6384837289bd58663e3436147a47d53c","tid":2106954,"uid":299501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:39:25.000Z","msg":"初選前有邊個拎搜查令掂過啲電腦？點解建制報紙最快有結果？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2106906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2106906</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"165f6f88d9afd0f86fa39c03900d2dc996dde5a0","tid":2106954,"uid":74683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"efed3ef6f0f87531800e6216ee668de6f646b058","tid":2106954,"uid":131121,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T14:38:22.000Z","msg":"算啦, pr當道, 連登仔普遍又缺乏批判思考<br />\n佢未當選已經假定佢一定會好似OMDB/BIG雲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /